title: General Motors to Participate in the J.P. Morgan Auto Conference
text:
General Motors to Participate in the J.P. Morgan Auto Conference Tue, Aug 11 2015 
General Motors will be participating in the J.P. Morgan Auto Conference on Tuesday, August 11, 2015 in New York City, New York. GM's presentation will begin at approximately 12:15 PM ET followed by a Q&A session. Representing GM will be:Â· Johan de Nysschen, Executive Vice President and President Global Cadillac A live webcast of the presentation will be available on this page. Shortly before the webcast, the presentation materials will be posted here.
